    <ImplicitInverseRef name="allSchemasInPatchArray" id="cb3f8c5e-8083-4234-a264-385f486d0bb6">
        <memberTypeInverse/>
        <type name="SchemaInPatchArray"/>
        <text>Maintains a list of scheams used by the patch in schema hierarchy order, by putting them into the array at their number below PortSchema.
(Meaning there will be a lot of null entries in this list)

Used to inform JSM of the correct order in which to load multiple schemas. (TFS #41865)</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
